{"tid":921863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【DG風波】「中國人衣服有毒」 疑似設計師發抵制言論再掀怒潮","createTime":"2018-11-30T02:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T13:03:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"50a6e0dcda0a9c294b60d0ae82996cd298fcc0f2","tid":921863,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"意大利奢侈品牌Dolce &amp; Gabbana（DG）近日因在廣告及社交言論中涉嫌公然辱華，掀起了軒然大波，中國藝人及網民紛紛聲討，更揚言要抵制DG的商品。隨後品牌兩名設計師拍片公開道歉，以圖平息事件，今日卻又傳出兩人疑似在社交平台上發佈「抵制中國」的言論，令風波再起。<br />\n<br />\n據意大利華人Luca爆料稱，這段挑釁中國的言論是於當地時間11月29日，在兩名設計師的個人Ig帳戶上發佈，並迅速引起了海外華人群體的高度關注，紛紛轉發。<br />\n<br />\nLuca指，言論以意大利文發表，原文繙譯是「如果中國人不買我們DG的產品，那就請所有的意大利人都別吃中餐，中國的衣服有毒，中國人喜歡偷稅漏稅，中國人的食品都是過期的，大家千萬不要購買任何中國的產品！」<br />\n<br />\n此番言論如同此前謾罵中國是「屎」一樣，很快引起了眾怒。不過，根據留學生媒體《郎言志》和意大利華人的反覆核實發現，這則這論很快被刪除了。隨後，有華人就此事致信DG官方，要求給出合理解釋，惟至今DG方面仍沒有就此言論發表任何官方回應。<br />\n<br />\n另有知情人士表示，由於相關內容被迅速刪除，所以並不能確定就是DG設計師所發，有DG的員工以私人名義稱：「這應該不是公司負責人。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181130/58974915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181130%2F58974915&d=JxDRBE6j8SgAGaAZIKTA0ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=511926a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181130%2F58974915&h=5d6b2211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181130/58974915</a>"},{"pid":"32b802c2429c20031d4bb29a500b03ba84089388","tid":921863,"uid":213441,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:34:00.000Z","msg":"人地有無講錯先"},{"pid":"b8c209deaa13bf6f9652b65151740ca5113a566a","tid":921863,"uid":27038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"32b802c2429c20031d4bb29a500b03ba84089388","tid":921863,"uid":213441,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:34:00.000Z","msg":"人地有無講錯先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"講中曬對支那傷害最大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76c9720e811bc44f8a3934acb0afc7f39c0c476","tid":921863,"uid":84734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b8c209deaa13bf6f9652b65151740ca5113a566a","tid":921863,"uid":27038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"32b802c2429c20031d4bb29a500b03ba84089388","tid":921863,"uid":213441,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:34:00.000Z","msg":"人地有無講錯先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"講中曬對支那傷害最大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:12:18.000Z","msg":"兩邊都咁柒<br />\n一邊走住黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另一邊得把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc3333c888421ecfafb41919564b9f04d47a86f","tid":921863,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T04:09:49.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"53678f9092974a79e2ef017bb3cc77ccda220764","tid":921863,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T04:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inUMR64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinUMR64.jpg&h=db69d901&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"653fd6d235030cfc2ed75c92655cbd572635c1fb","tid":921863,"uid":208159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10f8cbfabd0684de489ddcc95ed69eccc8032fcf","tid":921863,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3475a5bd45fe8278f84c2ae8ef9ac341d6fe2e9","tid":921863,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T04:19:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a7fc524a93d10df2270c46a60e54ebc67849783","tid":921863,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"